    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You focus chakra in 5-foot cube of earth you can see in range, creating a pillar that launches any willing creature above it to a point 30 feet in the air. If this jutsu would affect a non-willing creature then it must succeed a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed saving throw it is launched in the air.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, and increase the cube of affected earth by 5 feet and the distance launched in the air by 10 feet.</p>",
